comments: Irving (DAL) is firming up over his left foot and absorbs the contact from Sochan (SAS) during the pick.
Collins (SAS) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot, and he changes and moves his pivot foot on the perimeter.
Irving (DAL) brushes Collins' (SAS) arm and the contact on the perimeter is marginal.
Collins (SAS) turns slightly towards Green (DAL) and marginal contact occurs as the defensive switch occurs.
Lively II (DAL) raises his arm into Johnson's (SAS) arm prior to making any contact with the ball, and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Lively II (DAL) cleanly blocks Johnson's (SAS) shot near the rim.
Doncic (DAL) inititaes contact with Sochan's (SAS) arm, which causes Sochan to lose control of the ball.
Vassell (SAS) is turning away from Irving's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during Irving's shot attempt at the basket.
Doncic (DAL) is moving alongside Johnson's (SAS) path as they come together at the same spot during the drive.
Lively II's (DAL) left leg cleanly dislodges the ball from Johnson (SAS).
Lively II (DAL) attempts to secure the loose ball and marginal body contact occurs with Johnson (SAS) as the two come together on the ground.
Collins (SAS) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard Lively II (DAL).
Johnson (SAS) brushes Lively II's (DAL) right arm and marginal arm contact occurs as they pursue the rebound.
Lively II (DAL) makes clean contact with the ball as Collins (SAS) receives the pass.
Irving (DAL) brings his forearm towards Wembanyama's (SAS) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together at the same spot.
Williams (DAL) cleanly blocks Vassell's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
